data.title: EUFA Champions League Result and Ranking 2010-11
data.meta_description: EUFA Champions League Result and Ranking 2010-11 - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. Raul Gonzalez took his tally to 142 / 71 as FC Schalke 04 made club history by reaching the semi-finals and climbing from 53rd to 36th in the all-time ranking. After 130 UEFA Champions League games and 66 goals for Real madrid CF, the Spanish attacker took his total to 130 / 66.
